attributes.title: Cuillin Brewery Ltd
attributes.description:
Created on February 28, 2010 by leo on Sourcemap.org:

Born in September 2004, in the old public bar of the Sligachan Hotel.  Celebration ales brewed, regular brewing planned from Easter 2005.  Ales brewed for sale in Sligachan Hotel.
